I"'<div class="p">Lone bloom of lovely happenstance</div>
<div class="p">Upon the shores of being's expanse,</div>
<div class="p">Bestow new life on private sense,</div>
<div class="p">Bless with the musk of innocence,</div>
<div class="p">Give sacred gift of touch, bestow</div>
<div class="p">The sight of precious bibelot,</div>
<div class="p">Nor fade nor perish though the hour</div>
<div class="p">Of monstrous force and fatal power</div>
<div class="p">Befall and trounce the petals fair</div>
<div class="p">That wilt in every baneful air.</div>
